trans-unit.source: Provides a <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline"></xref> for media content.
trans-unit.target: Gir et <xref href="System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline"> </xref> for medieinnhold.

trans-unit.source: MediaTimeline is a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline> object which provides control over media timing in the same way that animation timeline objects control animations.
trans-unit.target: MediaTimeline er en <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline>objekt med kontroll over mediet tidsberegning på samme måte animasjonen tidslinjen objekter kontrollere animasjoner.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline>

trans-unit.source: For example, a MediaTimeline has associated <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Duration%2A> and <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.BeginTime%2A> properties can be used to specify when media begins and how long it plays.
trans-unit.target: For eksempel en MediaTimeline har tilknyttede <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Duration%2A>og <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.BeginTime%2A>egenskapene som kan brukes til å angi når mediet begynner og hvor lenge avspilling.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.BeginTime%2A> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Duration%2A>

trans-unit.source: See [Animation Overview](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) for more information on animation timelines.
trans-unit.target: Se [animasjonen oversikt over](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) for mer informasjon om animasjonen tidslinjer.

trans-unit.source: There are two ways to associate a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline> to a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement> using a MediaTimeline.
trans-unit.target: Det er to måter å knytte et <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline>til en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement>ved hjelp av en MediaTimeline.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline>

trans-unit.source: Inside of a <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>, when a MediaTimeline is targets a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement>, a <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaClock> will be created and assigned to the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement>’s associated player.
trans-unit.target: I for en <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>, når en MediaTimeline er rettet mot en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement>, en <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaClock>blir opprettet og tilordnet av <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement>tilknyttede player.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement> </xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaClock> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement> </xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Storyboard>

trans-unit.source: See [How to: Control a MediaElement by Using a Storyboard](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) for an example; 2.
trans-unit.target: Se [slik: kontrollere en MediaElement ved hjelp av en dreiebok](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md) et eksempel; 2.

trans-unit.source: By explicitly creating a <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaClock> from a MediaTimeline and assigning it to a <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement>.
trans-unit.target: Ved eksplisitt å opprette et <xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaClock>fra en MediaTimeline og tilordne den til en <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement> </xref:System.Windows.Media.MediaClock>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Duration%2A> of the MediaTimeline is set to `Automatic` (default), the duration of MediaTimeline is the natural duration of the media source.
trans-unit.target: Hvis den <xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Duration%2A>av MediaTimeline er satt til `Automatic` (standard), hvor lenge MediaTimeline er naturlig varigheten for datakilden media.</xref:System.Windows.Media.Animation.Timeline.Duration%2A>

trans-unit.source: To find the natural duration of the media source programmatically, query the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement.NaturalDuration%2A> property of the <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement>.
trans-unit.target: Du finner naturlig varigheten for datakilden media programmatisk ved spørring <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement.NaturalDuration%2A>for <xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement>.</xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement> </xref:System.Windows.Controls.MediaElement.NaturalDuration%2A>
